more than 25,000 LPs and 23,000 singles - for Pounds 181,694 yesterday,
comfortably exceeding the Pounds 150,000 estimate.
A private collector from St Louis in the US bought it by secret tender, and
the proceeds are to go to the Terrence Higgins Trust, the Aids charity.
