The 5,000 black and white images were sold, with full copyright, for Pounds
91,700 to Bloomsbury Publishing, which plans to use them as the basis for an
illustrated book.
The Sotheby's auction totalled Pounds 441,697 and was over 83 per cent sold
by value.
